OL,3,CZoe Thomas appointed as new Head of
OL,4,CNews and Programmes for ITV Cymru Wales
OL,6,FZoe Thomas has been appointed as the
OL,7,Fnew Head of News and Programmes for
OL,8,FITV Cymru Wales.
OL,10,FZoe has spent her entire career in ITV
OL,11,FNews, having joined HTV Wales as a
OL,12,Ftrainee in 1999.
OL,14,FSince 2018 she has been Editor of ITV
OL,15,FCymru Wales' English Language
OL,16,FProgrammes and responsible for some of
OL,17,Four most popular titles, including
OL,18,FWales This Week, Coast & Country and
OL,19,FSharp End.
