OL,3,CZoe Thomas appointed as new Head of
OL,4,CNews and Programmes for ITV Cymru Wales
OL,6,FMichael Jermey, Director of ITV News
OL,7,Fand Current Affairs, said: "Zoe has
OL,8,Fmade an enormously valuable
OL,9,Fcontribution to ITV Cymru Wales over
OL,10,Fmany years.
OL,12,F"She has wide experience across a
OL,13,Frange of programming and has
OL,14,Fdemonstrated impressive editorial
OL,15,Fleadership.
OL,17,F"I'm delighted that Zoe will be
OL,18,Fleading the whole ITV Cymru Wales team
OL,19,Fas we take up a new 10-year PSB
OL,20,Flicence."
