OL,3,CZoe Thomas appointed as new Head of
OL,4,CNews and Programmes for ITV Cymru Wales
OL,6,FZoe said: "If you'd have told me when
OL,7,FI walked through the gates of our old
OL,8,FHQ Culverhouse Cross for the first
OL,9,Ftime, that 25 years later I would
OL,10,Fbecome the Head of News and Programmes
OL,11,Fat ITV Cymru Wales, I would never have
OL,12,Fbelieved it.
OL,14,F"I've been immensely lucky in that
OL,15,Ftime to have done a range of different
OL,16,Fjobs, and I'm incredibly grateful for
OL,17,Fthe opportunities that I've had
OL,18,Fthroughout my career, and for the
OL,19,Fpeople who've helped and guided me
OL,20,Falong the way.
